# Updated behavior summary

## Retry success

* copy `failed/file.zip.pgp` → `outgoing_e-invoicing/file.zip.pgp`
* trigger CFT on `outgoing_e-invoicing/file.zip.pgp`
* delete matching failed files
* delete temporary outgoing retry copy

## Retry failure

* copy `failed/file.zip.pgp` → `outgoing_e-invoicing/file.zip.pgp`
* trigger CFT fails
* delete temporary outgoing retry copy
* original file remains in `failed/`

